    <name>NoLimitConnect</name>
    <summary>Social Network</summary>
    <description>
        <p>NoLimitConnect is a full featured social network.</p>
        <p>A independent social network designed to be hosted on any device with an internet connection.</p>
        <p>Major features:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Person to Person and plugin permissions: Ignore, Guest, Friend, Admin</li>
            <li>Push To Talk VOIP</li>
            <li>Stream shared media files</li>
            <li>Share and transfer files (No file size limit)</li>
            <li>Video Chat</li>
            <li>VOIP Voice Phone</li>
            <li>Messenger</li>
            <li>About Me user page</li>
            <li>Storyboard blog page</li>
            <li>Web Cam Server</li>
            <li>Media Player</li>
            <li>Chat Room host and client</li>
            <li>Random Connect host and client</li>
            <li>Group host and client</li>
        </ul>
    </description>
